"  This was left on my car in the parking lot of Bon Appetit Cafe on Williamson Street.
I went there for lunch with a friend (and have been there before as a customer) but they were closed.
We decided to take her car to go somewhere else for lunch and we took her car.
We were back within the hour and I found this on my windshield.
I was back just as they reopened for their dinner hours.There was no one in the restaurant yet.
